snippet.title: SNES Longplay [132] Phalanx:  The Enforce Fighter A-144
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by:  Tsunao

First off:  the US SNES version of this game has an EPIC boxart!!

Don't know anything about the plot. =X  I guess it deals with aliens...or something.

Playing through the SNES version of Phalanx on Funny (the hardest difficulty in the game.  The only difficulty I played was Easy.  Granted, I was a child.)  Savestates were abused for no deaths. =X  For most of the mid bosses and bosses, I spam the E weapon and try to keep Missile B.

If anyone knows anything about that password at the end, enlighten me, please. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
